		<title>13HOUSING</title>
		<content>   Chesterfield has several very large 
 housing estates, most of which were   
 built after the Second World War. A   
 recent survey showed:-                
                                       
                                       
                                       
{  36,451 private houses               
{   3,181 flats                        
{  15,009 council houses               
{     314 housing association homes    
{     403 business/employer owned homes
{      75 temporary (mobile) homes     
                                       
                                       
                                       
   Chesterfield was the first town in  
 the country to adopt the Town Planning
 Act of the 1920's.                    
                                       
                                       
                                       </content>
